{"tid":706562,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"kindle 新手上路求助","createTime":"2018-06-18T04:07:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-23T05:20:07.000Z","uid":18185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c271d6b979499ecd07681895c54627b6115a88d9","tid":706562,"uid":18185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T04:07:07.000Z","msg":"小弟買左二手kindle 8<br />\n睇左幾本書但係有以下問題，想巴打們教下我（做左好多功課求助無門）<br />\n1. Kindle email係咪會過濾封面？用天火轉直排既書啲封面冇晒<br />\n<br />\n2.係咪要直接用usb過書先入到封面？但係我部機detect唔到kindle,有叉電但冇連到電腦。爬文話要原裝usb先得，我部二手kindle果條應該係原裝但都唔得，點解決？<br />\n<br />\n3.試過calibre加封面，係work既，但係啲書變晒橫排，點搞？試過加左封面先再放入天火轉直，過到落機就冇左封面，先用天火轉直再加封面落機就會變番橫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n4.試過用calibre個橫轉直外掛諗住全部野喺果到搞晒，但試左無數次都係變左得啲標點橫轉直，啲字照舊打橫，點搞好<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我有封面控"},{"pid":"a96d85512764e85ee3a48ba746a325503ef7464a","tid":706562,"uid":18185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T04:14:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"adc0c1cfed0157c334b0ab9cb8f492e1ba73dad0","tid":706562,"uid":18185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a96d85512764e85ee3a48ba746a325503ef7464a","tid":706562,"uid":18185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T04:14:51.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T14:32:25.000Z","msg":"Pish求助<br />\n我用原裝線直接過落kindle就會睇唔到本書，出個咩error occurred"},{"pid":"ce1b351416aa93f85364b2b4cbe743e5d06e8804","tid":706562,"uid":21378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T08:50:09.000Z","msg":"kindlegen 打包 出 mobi , <br />\n多數封面都正常 番."},{"pid":"a76f651181b801e5eb7540738b6568b86f141144","tid":706562,"uid":4840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T05:18:29.000Z","msg":"昨天firmware升了5.9.6.1後，回覆正常了，還可自行加字體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd2d0cba8925a1df3d7f0db1aaa82a05001a5d19","tid":706562,"uid":4840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T05:20:07.000Z","msg":"我用天火轉直排加封面及用usb過kindle Paperwhite"}]}